        <div class="font-medium text-gray-900 text-sm">Paint Calculator for a Room</div>
        <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">Calculate how many gallons of paint you need for standard, smooth interior walls.</div>
      </a>
      <a href="/calculators/paint-textured-walls" class="block bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-400 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
        <div class="font-medium text-gray-900 text-sm">Paint Calculator for Textured Walls</div>
        <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">Adjust coverage rates and calculate paint specifically for heavy interior wall textures.</div>
      </a>
      <a href="/calculators/subfloor" class="block bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-400 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
        <div class="font-medium text-gray-900 text-sm">Subfloor Calculator</div>
